title: NPDES Inventory KCI 1 Edit Map
description:
This map contains the KCI_1 version of the State Highway Administration’s stormwater (NPDES) inventory.  It is used in Collector for field data collection, inspections, and QA/QC.  The editing app is also built using this web map.

Date Last Updated: 05/20/2018
snippet: Editor map for Collector in the KCI_1 version.
accessInformation: MDOT State Highway Administration, Office of Environmental Design, Office of Planning and Preliminary Engineering Data Governance Division, KCI Technologies, ECO Integration, Elliott Plack, eplack@sha.state.md.us
